title: Anything U Want
lyrics:
Julie on the bed as a warm night falls
Heavy on her skin
Ricky on the field with some makeup on
Heavy on his eyelids
I love you



Tell me everything that you want to hear

Tell me anything that you want to feel

Oh, I want you near it



I love you



Anything you want

Anything you need

Anything at all

I love you

I love you
